#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:157
msgid "Key and certificate management for the Administrator"
msgstr "Gestion des clés et des certificat de l'Administrateur"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:160
#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:230
#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:475
#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:683
#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:741
msgid "Context"
msgstr "Contexte"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:162
msgid "Packages and actions done by an :term:`Administrator` are signed so that only Trusted Administrators are authorized to manage the devices."
msgstr "Les paquets et actions de l'Administrateur sont signés pour n'autoriser que les :term:`Administrateurs` de confiance à intervenir sur les postes."

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:165
msgid "The WAPT :term:`Administrator` holds:"
msgstr "L':term:`Administrateur` de la solution WAPT a en sa possession :"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:167
msgid "a private 2048 bit *RSA* key that has been encrypted by the aes-256-cbc algorithm;"
msgstr "une clé privée *RSA* de 2048 bits chiffrée par l'algorithme aes-256-cbc ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:170
msgid "a *X509* certificate signed by an :term:`Certificate Authority` trusted by the :term:`Organization`;"
msgstr "un certificat *X509* signé par une :term:`Autorité de Certification` approuvée par l':term:`Organisation` ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:175
msgid "The process for creating the keys and signing, distributing and revocating the certificates are of the responsibility of the :term:`Organization` using WAPT; that process is beyond the functional perimeter of WAPT."
msgstr "Le processus d'émission de ces clés, la signature du certificat, la distribution et la révocation sont à la charge de l':term:`Organisation` utilisant WAPT et sortent donc du périmètre fonctionnel de WAPT."

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:179
msgid "However, to make the testing of WAPT easy, WAPT offers a function to generate a RSA key and its corresponding X509 certificate:"
msgstr "Cependant, pour facilement tester la solution, WAPT propose une fonction pour générer une clé RSA et un certificat X509 :"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:182
msgid "the generated RSA key is 2048bit long, encrypted with aes-256-cbc, encoded in PEM format and saved with a *.pem* extension;"
msgstr "la clé RSA générée est de 2048 bits, chiffrée par l'algorithme aes-256-cbc et encodée en format PEM avec l'extension *.pem* ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:185
msgid "the certificate is either self-signed, or signed by a Trusted Authority from whom we have received a key and a PEM formated certificate;"
msgstr "le certificat est soit autosigné, soit signé par une autorité dont on a à disposition la clé et le certificat en format PEM ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:188
msgid "if the certificate is self-signed, then its *KeyUsage* attribute contains the *keyCertSign* flag;"
msgstr "si le certificat est autosigné, son attribut *KeyUsage* comporte le flag *keyCertSign* ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:191
msgid "if the :term:`Administrator` is authorized by the :term:`Organization` to sign packages that contain python code (the presence of a :file:`setup.py` file is detected in the package), the *extendedKeyUsage* attribute of the certificate contains the **CodeSigning** flag;"
msgstr "si l':term:`Administrateur` est habilité par l':term:`Organisation` à signer des paquets contenant du code python (présence du fichier :file:`setup.py`), l'attribut du certificat *extendedKeyUsage* comporte le flag **CodeSigning** ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:196
msgid "the *X509* certificate is encoded and handed over to the :term:`Administrator` in PEM format with a *.crt* extension;"
msgstr "le certificat *X509* est encodé et remis à l':term:`Administrateur` en format PEM avec l'extension *.crt* ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:200
msgid "Validity of the Administrator's certificate"
msgstr "Validité du certificat de l'Administrateur"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:202
msgid "For WAPT version up to 1.5.0.12, WAPT agent does not verify the revocation state of the :term:`Administrator`'s certificate during the process of verifying the package, the attributes or the actions of the :term:`Administrator`."
msgstr "Jusqu'à la version 1.5.0.12 incluse, Le client WAPT ne gère pas la vérification de la révocation du certificat de l':term:`Administrateur` lors du processus de vérifcation des paquets, attributs et actions de l':term:`Administrateur`."

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:207
msgid "It only checks the dates of validity (*notValidBefore*/ *notValidAfter* attributes). The certificate is valid if (**Now** >= *notValidBefore* and **Now** <= *notValidAfter*)."
msgstr "Il ne vérifie que les dates de validité (attributs *notValidBefore* / *notValidAfter*). Le certificat est valide si (**Now** >= *notValidBefore* et **Now** <= *notValidAfter*)."

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:212
msgid "Authorizing the Administrator's certificate to sign a package"
msgstr "Autoriser le certificat de l'Administrateur à signer un paquet"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:214
msgid "The certificate used by the WAPT console to sign packages and actions is defined with the *personal_certificate_path* parameter in the section ``[global]`` of the file :file:`%LOCALAPPDATA%\\waptconsole\\waptconsole.ini`."
msgstr "Le certificat utilisé par la console WAPT pour signer les paquets et actions est défini avec le paramètre *personal_certificate_path* de la section ``[global]`` du fichier :file:`%LOCALAPPDATA%\\waptconsole\\waptconsole.ini`."

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:218
msgid "WAPT asks the :term:`Administrator` for his password and then searches a private key (encoded in PEM format) that matches a certificate amongst the :file:`.pem` files in the directory containing the certificates."
msgstr "WAPT demande à l':term:`Administrateur` son mot de passe pour permettre de rechercher la clé privée (encodée au format PEM) correspondant au certificat parmi les fichiers :file:`.pem` du répertoire contenant les certificats."

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:222
msgid "When signing a package, WAPT will refuse the certificate if the package contains a :file:`setup.py` file and the certificate is not a *CodeSigning* type."
msgstr "Lors de la signature de paquet, WAPT refusera le certificat si le paquet contient un fichier :file:`setup.py` et que le certificat n'est pas de type *CodeSigning*."

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:227
msgid "Managing the **WAPT agent's** key and certificate"
msgstr "Gérer les clés et certificats du **Client WAPT**"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:232
msgid "The WAPT client (:program:`waptservice`) uses RSA keys and X509 certificates to interact with the WAPT Server."
msgstr "Le client WAPT (:program:`waptservice`) utilise des clés RSA et un certificat X509 pour interagir avec le serveur WAPT."

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:235
msgid "The WAPT client certificate is used in the following situations:"
msgstr "Le certificat du client WAPT est utilisé dans les situations suivantes :"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:237
msgid "when updating the WAPT client status on the server (:command:`update_server_status`) **signing informations**;"
msgstr "lors de la mise à jour du statut du poste sur le serveur. (:command:`update_server_status`) : **signature des informations**"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:240
msgid "when the WAPT agent establishes a Websocket with the server (:program:`waptservice`) **signing the WAPT client UUID**;"
msgstr "lors de la connexion Websocket du poste vers le serveur (:program:`waptservice`) : **signature de l'UUID du poste**"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:244
msgid "First emission and later update of the WAPT agent's certificate"
msgstr "Émission initiale et mise à jour du certificat du client WAPT"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:246
msgid "on finishing the installation process of the WAPT agent on the device, the WAPT agent automatically registers itself on the WAPT Server by sending a Kerberos authenticated HTTPS request that uses the TGT of the machine account."
msgstr "à l'issu du processus d'installation de l'agent WAPT sur le Poste client, l'agent WAPT s'enregistre automatiquement auprès du serveur WAPT en émettant une requête https authentifiée par Kerberos qui utilise le TGT du compte machine ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:251
msgid "The WAPT agent uses Windows kerberos APIs implemented with :program:`kerberos-sspi` and :program:`requests-kerberos` python modules."
msgstr "L'agent WAPT utilise les API kerberos de Windows en s'appuyant sur les modules python :program:`kerberos-sspi` et :program:`requests-kerberos` ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:256
msgid "this process works if and only if the device is joined to the Windows domain for which the WAPT Server is configured."
msgstr "Cette procédure fonctionne si et seulement si le Poste client est joint au domaine Windows pour lequel le serveur WAPT est configuré."

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:259
msgid "if the key and the certificates have not yet been generated, or if they do not match the current :term:`FQDN` of the device, the WAPT agent generates a self-signed RSA key and X509 certificate with the following parameters:"
msgstr "si la clé et les certificats n'ont pas encore été générés, ou s'ils ne correspondent pas au :term:`FQDN` actuel de la machine, l'agent WAPT génère une clé RSA et un certificat X509 autosigné avec les paramètres suivants :"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:263
msgid "the key is 2048 bit RSA encoded in PEM format and stored in the file :file:`<WAPT>\\private\\<device FQDN>.pem`;"
msgstr "la clé est de type RSA 2048 bits encodée en PEM et stockée dans le fichier :file:`<WAPT>\\\private\\\<fqdn du poste>.pem` ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:266
msgid "the generated certificate has the following attributes:"
msgstr "le certificat généré a les attributs suivants :"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:268
msgid "*Subject.COMMON_NAME* = <device FQDN>;"
msgstr "*Subject.COMMON_NAME* = <device FQDN>;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:270
msgid "*Subject.ORGANIZATIONAL_UNIT_NAME* = name of the :term:`Organization` registered in the WAPT client's Windows registry;"
msgstr "*Subject.ORGANIZATIONAL_UNIT_NAME* = nom de l':term:`Organisation` de la machine tel qu'enregistré dans la base de registre ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:273
msgid "*SubjectAlternativeName.DNSName* = <device FQDN>;"
msgstr "*SubjectAlternativeName.DNSName* = <device FQDN> ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:275
msgid "*BasicConstraint.CA* = True;"
msgstr "*BasicConstraint.CA* = True ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:277
msgid "*validity* = 10 years;"
msgstr "*validity* = 10 ans ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:279
msgid "*serialnumber* = random;"
msgstr "*serialnumber* = aléatoire ;"

#: ../../source/wapt_security_principles/crypto.rst:281
msgid "the certificate is saved in the :file:`<WAPT>\\private\\<device FQDN>.crt`;"
msgstr "le certificat est sauvegardé dans le fichier :file:`<WAPT>\\private\\<device FQDN>.crt` ;"

